# Coding Challenges — Solutions by ip5en

How this repo is organized
- `challenges/` — each challenge has its own folder (see below)
- `challenges/<YYYY-MM-DD>-<slug>/README.md` — problem statement + metadata
- `challenges/<YYYY-MM-DD>-<slug>/<language>/solution.<ext>` — solution file (one or more)
- `challenges/<YYYY-MM-DD>-<slug>/tests/` — optional tests for CI / local verification
